data.description: Presented for sale is this ''better than new'' single-family home in the desirable subdivision of Ruffin's River Landing! Built in late 2022, this home has been very well cared for, lightly lived in, and ready for new owners! Situated on a large semi-private lot, you will be immediately impressed by the tree lined back yard and mature landscape surrounding this home. A welcoming front entry opens up to a beautiful open-concept design boasting luxury vinyl plank flooring, crown molding, and 9 foot ceilings. The kitchen features a large center island, stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash, granite counter tops, and ample cabinet space. The large living room adjoining the kitchen makes this home ideal for entertaining guests. Entering the private owners suite at the back of the house you will be immediately impressed with the spacious bathroom and walk in closet. Two additional bedrooms and a second full bath round out the interior space. Off the back of the living room is a cute deck overlooking the natural landscape of the back yard that is perfect for grilling out or relaxing on a peaceful evening. A full 2-car garage provides plenty of space for your vehicles and additional storage for your all of your beach toys. Located just 10 minutes from Holden Beach you will love calling this coastal getaway your forever home. Call today for a private showing!
